A. BE
   - Fetches and stores xrates from fintech providers by making API calls or raw http GET requests or selenium/automation
   - Provides webservide API data endpoints for UI clientes
   - Caters for redundant servers for failproof service and load balancing
   - Multithreaded Java and C/C++, PHP
   
B. FE
   - Calls API data endpoints provided by the servers
   - Calculates and shows forex stats and graphs
   - Desktop Win and MacOS, website, Android, iOS
